EUROPE; EASTERN EUROPE -- DEFENSE; EASTERN EUROPE -- SECURITY; NORTH ATLANTIC 
TREATY ORGANIZATION; EUROPE -- SECURITY; UNITED STATES -- ARMED FORCES -- 
