-- LUXEMBOURG; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- LUXEMBOURG; BANK ACCOUNTS; 
BANK OF CREDIT AND COMMERCE INTERNATIONAL; AWAN, AMJAD 
</P>
