Photo, Dr. George Seeds is taken from Santa Monica Hospital for transfer to 
Torrance Memorial Hospital's burn center after he was attacked with acid. His 
assailant, a 74-year-old man, died in the struggle. LISA ROMERIN / Los Angeles 
Times; Photo, George M. Seeds 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
