<HEADLINE>
<P>
FIGHTING BIGOTRY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Times should be congratulated for its excellent article on the Los Angeles 
County Human Relations Commission (Jan. 2). 
</P>
<P>
Every agency in our community that deals with diversity and discrimination 
counts on the commission as a source of information and expertise. 
</P>
<P>
The commission's assistance and cooperation were instrumental in helping the 
ADL launch our media, school and community-based prejudice reduction campaign, 
"A World of Difference." 
</P>
<P>
On numerous other matters the commission has been of great help and is a valued 
part of our diverse society. 
</P>
<P>
We salute the Times and the commission. 
</P>
<P>
NORMAN EPSTEIN 
</P>
<P>
Chairman 
</P>
<P>
Executive Committee 
</P>
<P>
Anti-Defamation League 
</P>
