contributions to the town, where several of her relatives live. The 1989 
Legislature approved a resolution renaming the road. 
</P>
<P>
Wynette, who lives in Nashville, Tenn., held a concert last year to benefit Red 
Bay School. Wynette said the only other thing that bears her name is a park in 
her husband's hometown of Malden, Mo. 
